<h1 id="13주차-성능-분석과-관찰성-perfflame-graph">13주차: 성능 분석과 관찰성 (perf·Flame Graph)</h1>

<p><img src="/Users/hojin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/28d2e8ff-2bf4-4b06-8f22-23880f1f7300/ai_os_13.png" alt="OS Core Architecture" />
